newsitem.title: INDONESIA: Bank Indonesia supplies 699 bln rph temporarily.
newsitem.headline: Bank Indonesia supplies 699 bln rph temporarily.

text.p: Indonesia's central bank, Bank Indonesia, supplied some 699 billion rupiah temporarily on the money market early on Wednesday, money traders said.

Some 962 billion rupiah of central bank certificates (SBIs) were due today, compared with some 113 billion rupiah of maturing short-term papers (SBPUs) and 150 billion rupiah of SBIs to be settled today.
